name: St. John
description:
John McAfee did not commit suicide.
He stated on numerous occasions he was in no way suicidal and actually enjoyed his incarceration in ways. 
Upon his passing, a timer was triggered, a so called "dead man's switch" set to release 30+TB of incriminating evidence on numerous targets. Today is the day that countdown ends, and we can only wait and see what is revealed but one thing is certain, John McAfee knows a thing or two about cyber security.

R.I.P. McAfee, they will never uninstall you
